# Get Booking

This endpoint retrieves the details of all bookings.

## Request

- Method: GET

- URL: `https://restful-booker.herokuapp.com/booking`


## Response

The response for this request is a JSON object representing the details of all bookings. You can refer to the JSON schema below to understand the structure of the response.

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "bookingid": {
      "type": "number"
    },
    "booking": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "firstname": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "lastname": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "totalprice": {
          "type": "number"
        },
        "depositpaid": {
          "type": "boolean"
        },
        "bookingdates": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "checkin": {
              "type": "string",
              "format": "date"
            },
            "checkout": {
              "type": "string",
              "format": "date"
            }
          }
        },
        "additionalneeds": {
          "type": "string"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```

### Create a New Booking

This API endpoint allows you to create a new booking.

#### Request Body

- `firstname` (string, required): The first name of the guest.

- `lastname` (string, required): The last name of the guest.

- `totalprice` (number, required): The total price of the booking.


#### Response

The response will be in JSON format and will contain the following properties:

``` json
{
  "bookingid": 0,
  "booking": {
    "firstname": "",
    "lastname": "",
    "totalprice": 0,
    "depositpaid": true,
    "bookingdates": {
      "checkin": "",
      "checkout": ""
    },
    "additionalneeds": ""
  }
}

 ```

#### JSON Schema for Response

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "bookingid": {
      "type": "number"
    },
    "booking": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "firstname": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "lastname": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "totalprice": {
          "type": "number"
        },
        "depositpaid": {
          "type": "boolean"
        },
        "bookingdates": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "checkin": {
              "type": "string"
            },
            "checkout": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          }
        },
        "additionalneeds": {
          "type": "string"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```

### Get Booking Details

This endpoint retrieves the details of a specific booking identified by the unique booking ID.

#### Request

- Method: GET

- URL: `https://restful-booker.herokuapp.com/booking/:id`

- Path Parameters:

    - `id`: The unique identifier of the booking.


#### Response

The response for this request is a JSON object representing the details of the booking. The JSON schema for the response can be found below:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "bookingid": {
      "type": "integer"
    },
    "booking": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "firstname": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "lastname": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "totalprice": {
          "type": "integer"
        },
        "depositpaid": {
          "type": "boolean"
        },
        "bookingdates": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "checkin": {
              "type": "string",
              "format": "date"
            },
            "checkout": {
              "type": "string",
              "format": "date"
            }
          }
        },
        "additionalneeds": {
          "type": "string"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```
